This repository documents architectural extensions developed in production
use of a multi-agent Claude Code fleet. The primary artifact is README.md,
which doubles as the gist-form writeup.

The integrity layer (Section 19 of the README) is the load-bearing contribution.
If you are building or operating a multi-agent LLM system, start there.
